---
title: Roast Duck & Romesco Sauce with Parmesan-Veggie Risoni & Rocket Balsamic Salad
description: Duck loves an equally rich companion and it’s going to tingle your tastebuds as you bite into its crispy skin with a smokey
romesco sauce. The light, classic combination of bitter rocket and Parmesan in the risoni cuts through the richness as well, giving
you a dinner that’s sure to leave you feeling fancy.
